kio_slp is a kde ioslave that uses OpenSLP.  It takes URL's
like service: ftp and will display all locations where that service
is running.  Konqueror will display the results, and clicking on
a service location will redirect you to that location, if there
is an installed ioslave to handle that protocol.

The requires the latest & greates kde2 and qt releases.

To build:
make -f Makefile.cvs
./configure  --prefix=<your-kde2-dir> --with-qt-dir=<your qt2.2 dir>
make
make install

run ./configure --help to see other configuration options.
